profile:
Established in 2016, Lincoln Property Maintenance is a small business based in Pickering Village (Ajax), Ontario that thrives on customer satisfaction and professionalism. We understand that owning a property comes with many responsibilities and jobs that can be overwhelming. Our main goal is to help make some of those jobs easier and stress-free. We offer a wide-range of services. 



Owner Ian De Clute has over 15 years of experience in general contracting in the Greater Toronto Area. He works extensively with property owners and managers on residential, condominium, and commercial properties. Ian works together with his clients to understand their needs and develop customized solutions that best achieve clients' goals and satisfaction. Ian prides himself on professionalism and attention to detail to achieve high-quality results.



Please contact us for more information - we'd love to hear from you!


Experienced property maintenance service and general contractor serving homeowners and property management companies in Durham Region, Ontario.

Visit us at www.lincolnpropertymaintenance.ca

profile:
We Specialize in Property Clean-ups, for Clients who are Fed Up with Lingering Junk. The MORE we HAUL away the LESS you PAY. Don't Hesitate Call or Book Online Today! 289-600-4646 - JWDREMOVAL.NET. 

We also help customers who are getting ready to sell their homes and need help in preparing their properties for resale. We offer a pay by the pound system with the only Rewards Program in Durham Region. 

• PAY-BY-THE-POUND NOT BY VOLUME/SPACE. 
• FAST & FREE ONLINE BOOKING 
• RESCHEDULE ANYTIME! 
• NO OBLIGATIONS 
• NO CREDIT CARD REQUIRED 
• PAYMENT OPTIONS - Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Diners Club, Paypal, E-Transfer, Cash 
• REWARDS PROGRAM 

We ensure that your junk gets recycled, donated or disposed of responsibly We take all the steps to separate, segregate and recycle anything that we haul away from your home & business. 

Anything that we can donate will be given to good will and other charities that get in touch with us. All books received are donated to homeless shelters in need of them. 

Service Locations: Oshawa, Whitby and Courtice 

We are a family owned & operated business Located in Oshawa. 

Website: JWDREMOVAL.NET 

Little Message From James William Dalby - Current Owner 
8/7/2015 
"Hi, My name is James I am the owner of this business and I created this business to help people in the local oshawa area. I have many tools at my disposal and I work hard everyday to improve the structure of this business. I strive to achieve better standards in the junk removal industry for my customers. I am highly focused on aquiring new equipment daily and tools to help clients with special needs as well. We are simply a small family owned & operated business located in Oshawa. I worked very hard on designing my website and I work hard to make it better everyday to better serve my customers needs. We have many free tools in place on our website to serve you and make the processing and booking of your junk removal appointment much easyier. We care about each of you as a customer and our goal is to proove to you that you can come to us time and time again and remember that with our rewards program that you will always save by choosing J.W.D for future visits as well or even your family & friends. Our pay by the pound system allows people to get an honest estimate that is 100% accurate to the weight taken away. This business is not only my sole source of income but my chance at a better life, I created this company from nothing with nothing. From nothing I created everything and the future in mind my goals are going to become more and more ambitious. But truth be told starting my own business was not as easy as it sounds and I have many hurdles to get over to get to the finish line. I have great character but I lack people skills and I also have PTSD and Bi-Polar. So creating this was not only a dream but my only chance at a real future with some means to an end. I am not so great in public places and large amounts of people but one on one I can shine and show my true potential to any client. "
